task.summary: Worked through pandas online tutorial. Changed theme
Added naive seasonal forecast method, and autocorrelation plots to identify seasonality.
Added resampling techniques, and Simple Exponential Smoothing
Added Holt, Damped Holt, and Holt-Winters forecasting.
Converted (seasonally) differenced forecasts back to actual forecasts, and computed error statistics on those.
Added another forecasting method, which creates seasonal indices and then uses these to convert data into seasonally adjusted data, on which SES etc is performed, before the data is converted back.
Refactored some of the helper code into different files, and added the comb and comb_adjusted forecasting methods.
Refactored a lot of code. Added the general test function. Checked that seasonal decomposition is correct (it is).
